  "translations": {
    "en": "And the right of prayer is that you know it is an arrival before Allah, Mighty and Majestic, and that you are standing before Allah. When you know that, you will stand in the station of the lowly, vile, beseeching, fearful, hopeful, afraid, abased, imploring one, magnifying the One before whom you stand with stillness and dignity. You approach it with your heart and perform it within its bounds and rights.",
